---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="CV" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    <p>
      I am a Computer Systems Engineering student at the <a
        href="https://www.ues.edu.sv/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-sky-600 underline">University of El Salvador.</a
      > I consider myself a self-taught person, passionate about technology and web
      development. I like to learn new things and face challenges that allow me to
      grow professionally.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="FullStack Developer at WOWTV"
      subtitle="From September, 2024 to present in WOWTV CMS"
    >
      Since September 2024, I have been working on the development of a project
      called WOWTV CMS <a href="/projects/wow-tv" class="text-sky-600 underline"
        >see project</a >, a Content Management System for a streaming platform.
      <br /><br />
      As a lead Full Stack developer:
      <br />
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
        <li>I led the development team, using tools such as Jira and GitHub to manage the project.</li>
        <li>Implemented and configured the content management system using Strapi CMS.</li>
        <li>Developed the frontend using Astro, React and TailwindCSS.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="FullStack Developer at ChivoTour"
      subtitle="From February 2023 to December 2023 in ChivoTour Project"
    >
      During 2023, I participated in the development of a project called
      ChivoTour
      <a href="/projects/chivotour" class="text-sky-600 underline"
        >see project</a
      >, a website for Tourist Sites in El Salvador. My main role was to develop
      the module for uploading new tourist sites. I used technologies such as
      Quasar, Firebase, and CouchDB. This project allowed me to gain
      comprehensive experience in both frontend and backend development,
      understanding the entire lifecycle of a web application, from creating
      mockups to deploying to production.
      <br /><br />
      Through this project, I learned:
      <br />
      <ul class="list-disc mx-6 grid gap-2">
        <li>Good development practices.</li>
        <li>
          Effective collaboration within a team of developers, working on a
          shared repository on GitHub.
        </li>
        <li>
          Agile development methodologies, actively participating in sprints.
        </li>
        <!-- <li>Además, desarrollo mis propios proyectos personales para seguir mejorando mis conocimientos en el desarrollo web.</li> -->
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Computer Systems Engineering"
      subtitle="2020 to present at Universidad de El Salvador, Santa Ana, El Salvador"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="General Baccalaureate"
      subtitle="2018 to 2019 Complejo Educativo Católico María Auxiliadora, Santa Ana, El Salvador"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="/Certificado-Fusalmo.pdf" target="_blank"
        >Backend Web Development (188 hours) - Fusalmo <span
          class="text-sky-600 underline">See certificate</span
        ></a
      >
    </li>
    <!-- <li>
      <a href="#" target="_blank"> Certification Name (with link)</a>
    </li> -->
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Languages</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>JavaScript</li>
    <li>Java</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">
      Frameworks, Libraries, and Execution Environments
    </div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>Node.js</li>
    <li>Express</li>
    <li>Astro Framework</li>
    <li>React</li>
    <li>Vue.js</li>
    <li>Quasar</li>
    <li>SocketIO</li>
    <li>Moongose</li>
    <li>JWT</li>
    <li>OAuth 2.0</li>
    <li>TailwindCSS</li>
    <li>Strapi CMS</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Databases</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>MongoDB</li>
    <li>MySQL</li>
    <li>CouchDB</li>
    <li>Firebase</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Development Tools</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>Docker</li>
    <li>Git</li>
    <li>GitHub</li>
    <li>Visual Studio Code</li>
    <li>Figma</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Testing Tools</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>Jest</li>
    <li>Postman</li>
    <li>Selenium</li>
  </ul>
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-xl w-full font-bold">Cloud Services</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>AWS</li>
    <li>Heroku</li>
    <li>Netlify</li>
    <li>MongoDB Atlas</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Languages</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-3 columns-2 mx-6 mb-5">
    <li>Spanish - Native</li>
    <li>English - Intermediate</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
